screen_desc: The screenshot displays a food delivery app interface showing the user's cart from "Bradman Pizza house." It lists a 9-inch Supreme pizza priced at $14.95, with an option to add more items. Below, there are suggestions to complement the cart, including a Meat Lovers pizza ($14.95), Garlic Bread ($5.20), Cheesecake ($7.50), and a Chocolate Mousse. A summary section indicates a promotion to add $5.05 for a 20% discount, and a prominent "Continue" button is available for proceeding with the order.
